Basic commands 
Container is a running environment for image
port binded : talk to application running inside of container 
virtual file system

docker pull 'name' ##first time run 
docker run 'name'
or docker run 'name':4.0 #para rodar uma versão específica
docher ps = list of dockers running

docker run -d 'name'
docker stop 'ID'
docker ps -a #lista os processsos que foram fechados 
docker start 'ID'
